headline: Has Caterpillar (CAT) Rallied Too Far After Strong Multi Year Share Price Gains
summary: If you are wondering whether Caterpillar's current share price still reflects good value or if the stock has run too far, this article walks through the key numbers in a plain spoken way. Caterpillar's share price recently closed at US$742.83, with returns of 13.0% over 30 days, 24.1% year to date, 118.9% over 1 year, 205.5% over 3 years and 270.0% over 5 years, which naturally raises questions about risk, reward and what is already priced in.
